summary: An ordinance approving an assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2196 for improvement of the alley in block 29, Capitol Hill Addition to the City of Seattle, Division No. 4, being the alley from East Highland Drive to East Galer Street, and between 15th Avenue North and 16th Avenue North, by grading and paving the same with asphalt, under Ordinance No. 21840, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof
